title: Issues in Toxicology
description:
Publisher: The Royal Society of Chemistry
ISSN: 1757-7179
Series Editors:
Professor Diana Anderson, University of Bradford, UK
Dr Michael D Waters, National Institute of Environmental Health Science, N Carolina, USA
Dr Timothy C Marrs, Food Standards Agency, London, UK

This Series is devoted to coverage of modern toxicology and assessment of risk and is responding to the resurgence in interest in these areas of scientific investigation. Ideal as a reference and guide to investigations in the biomedical, biochemical and pharmaceutical sciences at the graduate and post graduate level
